title: 'Great Aesthetics
body: '5.0 out of 5 stars''Have re-ordered this same product probably 2-3 times now. It comes in a pack of 3 (3 notebooks).  - It looks and feels great. The brown cover is just the perfect shade of brown. gives you that wintery/autumn feeling.  - Pages are absolute white and blank (not yellowish or any other warm tint). Pure white and decently thick. Using a fountain pen on the pages doesnt leave an impression on the back side  - The spiral binding is great and sturdy  Overall a good purchase if you want a plain blank white paged notebook that looks minimal and clean'
